seo_data.meta_title: Curl Defining Shampoo for Kids’ Curly Hair | Johnson's® Baby
seo_data.meta_description: Every coil, spiral and cute curlicue deserves to be shiny and strong. This gentle shea butter formula smooths frizz and adds definition to your child’s curls for 24 hours. We’ve even made sure this kids shampoo for curly hair is gentler than adult shampoo, but still delivers the luscious bounce each swirl and curl deserves. Ophthalmologist- and pediatrician-tested NO MORE TEARS® formula Hypoallergenic No parabens, phthalates, sulfates, or dyes Available in: 13.6 FL Oz.
